      "content": "self care wont stop the glaciers from melting or the oceans from rising. it's like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. i look at people talking about retirement plans or kids and i just feel... empty. how can anyone be so delusional? it feels like we're all just waiting for the end, and honestly, i'm tired of waiting.",
